Wings
The first equiment is wings which are made of special materials for the sport. The wing models to be used vary according to the weather conditions. 

Ropes
Second equipment is ropes where it divided into to suspension ropes and brake ropes. Although the ropes look very thin, they are capable of carrying a lot of weight.

Harness
Third equipment is harness functions as the pilot seat when paragliding.

Helmet
Forth equipment is a helmet that act as a precaution for any accidents.

Sunglasses
A pair of sunglasses to protect our eyes from the sun.

